---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Tentang Saya — Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani">
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Tentang Saya</h1>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 items-start mb-16">
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Potret profesional Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover" 
            loading="lazy"
            width="800"
            height="800"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 text-black/80 dark:text-white/80">
        <div class="space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-black dark:text-white">
            From heavy machinery to clean code — I build systems that work.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Saya Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani, seorang software developer yang memulai karier dari dunia yang sangat berbeda: sebagai operator excavator profesional. Selama bertahun-tahun bekerja di lapangan, saya belajar pentingnya presisi, sistem yang handal, dan tanggung jawab terhadap hasil kerja. Prinsip-prinsip itu kini saya terapkan dalam pengembangan perangkat lunak.
          </p>

          <p>
            Transisi ke tech bukan kebetulan — ini adalah pilihan strategis. Saya melihat paralelisme antara membangun infrastruktur fisik dan digital: keduanya membutuhkan perencanaan matang, eksekusi presisi, dan pemeliharaan jangka panjang. Bedanya, di software, saya bisa membangun sistem yang melayani ribuan pengguna secara simultan dengan biaya operasional minimal.
          </p>

          <p>
            Fokus saya ada pada <strong>full-stack development</strong> dengan spesialisasi di backend automation dan system architecture. Saya sangat tertarik dengan proyek yang menggabungkan AI, real-time systems, dan scalable infrastructure. Setiap line code yang saya tulis mengikuti prinsip: <em>modular, testable, maintainable</em>.
          </p>

          <p>
            Saat ini saya fokus membangun aplikasi production-ready dengan tech stack modern: <strong>Node.js</strong> untuk backend, <strong>React/Next.js</strong> untuk frontend, dan <strong>Redis</strong> untuk state management. Saya juga aktif mengintegrasikan <strong>AI (Google Gemini)</strong> untuk automation dan natural language processing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Highlight Achievements</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-accent mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span>Built WhatsApp e-commerce bot handling 100+ daily customers with 99% uptime</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-accent mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span>Achieved 99.7% test coverage (1121 tests) with comprehensive CI/CD pipeline</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-accent mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span>Reduced AI costs by 97% through strategic model selection (Gemini vs GPT-4)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-accent mt-0.5">▸</span>
              <span>Optimized VPS deployment for 2GB RAM constraint (300-500MB usage)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Tech Stack & Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Frontend Development</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['React 18','Next.js 14','Astro','TypeScript','Tailwind CSS','Framer Motion'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Backend & APIs</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['Node.js 20','Express','REST API','WhatsApp API','Webhook Systems','Cron Jobs'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">AI & Automation</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['Google Gemini','Vercel AI SDK','NLP','Intent Classification','Prompt Engineering'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Database & Storage</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['Redis','PostgreSQL','File-based Systems','Session Management'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Testing & Quality</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['Jest','Supertest','Unit Testing','Integration Tests','CI/CD','ESLint'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">DevOps & Deployment</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
            {['Git','GitHub Actions','PM2','VPS Management','Vercel','CDN'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Core Principles</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">
            <li>• Modular architecture dengan single responsibility</li>
            <li>• Test-driven development (80%+ coverage)</li>
            <li>• Performance optimization untuk low-resource environments</li>
            <li>• Security-first approach (input validation, XSS prevention)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Currently Learning</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">
            <li>• Advanced AI prompt engineering techniques</li>
            <li>• Microservices architecture patterns</li>
            <li>• Real-time data streaming (WebSockets)</li>
            <li>• Cloud-native development (AWS/GCP)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a href="/resume.pdf" class="px-4 py-2 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 rounded hover:border-accent text-xs">Unduh Resume</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
